casebody.data:
Sara E. PARKER
v.
RALEIGH BONDED MOVING SYSTEM RALEIGH BONDED WAREHOUSE. No. 380P04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 6, 2004. Sara E. Parker, Pro Se. William C. Smith, Jr., Raleigh, for Raleigh Bonded Warehouse.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Plaintiff on the 30th day of July 2004 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 6th day of October 2004."
